commit.message:
Simple bug fixes

Fixed app crashing when empty fields were entered. Also added a spinner to MainActivity.

User selection

Spinner added to registration page so user can select who they are

User types defined

Added TeacherMainActivity and StudentMainActivity for different app features.

HomeApplication added

Added a Java class to ensure that the user is logged out properly.

Master branch created

User login, registration, and password reset completed. Basic user profile outlined.
